ater 1.5L\n\n[Directions]\n\n1. Cut the radish into 3-cm thin pieces.\n2. Remove blood from beef.\n3. Chop or cut the green onion diagonally. Slice the onion.\n4. Add sesame oil and cooking oil to a pan and stir-fry the beef.\n5. Once the outside of the beef is cooked, add the cut radish.\n6. When the meat is cooked, add water, minced garlic, soup soy sauce, and fermented anchovy sauce, and simmer for 20 minutes over medium heat.\n7. Once the beef softens, add onion and keep simmering.\n8. Season with salt and finish with green onion and pepper.\n\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nBeef and mushroom soup\n\n[Ingredients]\n\nRadish 1&1/2 cup (230g)\nBeef for bulgogi 2/3 cup (100g)\n3 button mushrooms (180g)\nSesame oil 1 tbsp (8g)\nCooking oil 1 tbsp (8g)\nGreen onion 1/3 cup (30g)\n1 egg (50g)\nMinced garlic 1 tbsp (15g)\nSoup soy sauce 2 tbsp (20g)\nFermented anchovy sauce 2 tbsp (20g)\nFine salt 1/2 tbsp (5g)\nPepper\nWater 1.5L\n\n\n[Directions]\n\n1. Cut the radish into 3-cm thin pieces.\n2. Remove blood in beef meat and slice button mushrooms thinly.\n3. Chop or cut the green onion diagonally. Beat the egg in a bowl.\n4. Add sesame oil and cooking oil to a pan and stir-fry the beef.\n5. Once the beef is cooked halfway, add the cut radish.\n6. When the meat is cooked, add 1.5L of water, minced garlic, soup soy sauce, and fermented anchovy sauce, and simmer over medium heat.\n7. Once the radish is completely cooked, remove from the soup, and add button mushroom and water. Keep simmering.\n8. Season with salt and add beaten egg and green onion.\n9. Put in a bowl and finish with some pepper.\n\n\n한식을 사랑하는 외국인분들을 위해 외국어 자막을 첨부하였습니다.\n본 영상의 자막은 통합 언어 플랫폼 ‘플리토’와 함께 합니다.\nSubtitles in foreign languages are provided for everyone who loves Korean food.\nAll subtitles are provided by an integrated language platform, Flitto.\nhttps://www.flitto.com/business/video...','소고기 무국! 이거 하나면 국을 20가지는 만들 수 있습니다. ㅣ 백종원의 쿠킹로그'),(872,'/watch?v=3XYDL0oV9HQ','#백종원 #맛남의광장 #홍게라면\n맛남의 광장 강릉 옥계휴게소 편에 나온 홍게라면입니다.\n강릉까지 가시기 어렵다면 집에서 홍게라면의 맛과 비주얼을 즐겨보세요!\n\n=================================\n\n[양념장재료]\n\n된장 6큰술(90g)\n고춧가루3큰술(15g)\n국간장3큰술(30g)\n식용유 6큰술(45g)\n대파 2/3컵(50g)\n\n[양념장 만드는 법]\n\n1. 냄비에 식용유를 두르고 파를 넣어 파기름을 낸다.\n2. 된장을 넣어 볶은 후 고춧가루를 넣어 볶아준다.\n3. 국간장을 넣고 끓여 완성한다.\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n[홍게라면재료]\n\n홍게 1마리\n불린미역 적당량\n라면 1개\n양념장 2큰술(40g)\n물800ml\n\n[홍게라면 만드는 법]\n\n1. 미역을 물에 불려 한입크기로 잘라둔다.\n2. 대파는 송송썬다.\n3. 홍게는 배딱지, 아가미를 뜯어낸 후 2등분하여 세척한다.\n4. 냄비에 물을 넣고 끓으면 라면스프, 양념장, 미역, 홍게를 넣는다.\n5. 냄비에 비해 홍게가 너무 클 경우에는 가위를 이용하여 잘라준다.\n5. 물이 끓어오르면 면을 넣고 익혀 완성한다.\n\n\n[Sauce ingredients]\n\nSoybean paste 6 tbsp (90g)\nRed pepper powder 3 tbsp (15g)\nSoup soy sauce 3 tbsp (30g)\nCooking oil 6 tbsp (45g)\nGreen onion 2/3 cup (50g)\n\n[Directions for sauce]\n\n1. Add cooking oil to a pan and infuse with green onion.\n2. Add soybean paste and red pepper powder, and stir-fry.\n3. Add soup soy sauce to finish.\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n[Ingredients for snow crab ramyun]\n\n1 snow crab\nSoaked seaweed\n1 ramyun\nSauce 2 tbsp (40g)\nWater 800ml\n\n[Directions]\n\n1. Soak seaweed in water and cut into bite size.\n2. Chop green onion finely.\n3. Pry off the abdomen shell and gill, cut into half, and clean.\n4. Bring water to boil in a pot, add ramyun seasoning, sauce, seaweed, and snow crab.\n5. If the snow crab is too big for a pot, cut into smaller pieces with scissors.\n5. When the soup boils, add ramyun noodles and cook.\n\n\n한식을 사랑하는 외국인분들을 위해 외국어 자막을 첨부하였습니다.\n본 영상의 자막은 통합 언어 플랫폼 ‘플리토’와 함께 합니다.\nSubtitles in foreign languages are provided for everyone who loves Korean food.\nAll subtitles are provided by an integrated language platform, Flitto.\nhttps://www.flitto.com/business/video...','SBS 맛남의 광장 \'홍게라면\' 레시피를 공개합니다! ㅣ 백종원의 쿠킹로그'),(873,'/watch?v=j0-_vTbLALM','#백종원 #감자 #감자스프\n감자 농가 화이팅! 오늘은 감자 스프입니다.\n\n========